Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.74,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,さあ　もう一つ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.74,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.25,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,この…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.25,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:42.38,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,はい　上
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.40,0:02:42.38,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,来 上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:43.42,TEXT JP,,0,0,0,,はい　中
